channel.description:
[u][b][size=36pt]LegendScape V1.0 Development Team[/size][/b][/u]
[u][b][font=arial][size=14pt]What I'm Looking For[/size][/font][/b][/u]
[ul][li]Web Developer[/li] [li]Java Developer[/li][/ul]
[ul][li]Coder(Who can help me code)[/li] [li]Webclient Maker[/li][/ul]
[b][u][size=14pt] What will be given[/size][/u][/b]
[ul][li]Java Developer = Co-Owner[/li] [li]Web Developer = Head Admin[/li] [li]Coder = Admin/ Mod[/li] [li]Webclient Maker = Hidden Admin/Mod[/li][/ul]
[center][u][b]FEATURES[/b][/u][/center]
[ul][li]Nothing Big Simple DeltaScape server with an original runescape feel to it I removed most the teles[/li] [li]There is no skillzone because 70% of fishing spots and 90% of the mining rocks are coded I also fixed woodcutting[/li] [li]I added donator items such as Cyan whip, Gold whip, adamant whip- I will soon add donator ticket exchange for item[/li] [li]I made it where only one ip can log in at a time and I am working on removing dupes[/li][/ul]
